{
  "texts": [
    "In order to carry out our scoping review, we conducted a Google Scholar search for papers related to LLMs and video games published between 2020 to 2023 (and very early 2024).",
    "We used Google Scholar as it includes a wide variety of sources and publication types and allows full text search.",
    "We conducted our search on 15 January 2024, using the search string \"(LLM OR LLMs OR \"large language model\" OR \"large language models\") AND (\"video game\" OR \"video games\" OR videogame OR videogames)\" for the period 2020 to 2024.",
    "We used a full text search (rather than title or abstract only).",
    "Our search returned 2260 results, which we sorted by relevance."
  ]
}